videos.description: Allen Flanigan zips a pass to Isaac Okoro, who dishes to Jamal Johnson for the wide-open three pointer.

videos.headline: Auburn's great ball movement sets up Johnson's three

videos.description: Auburn's Danjel Purifoy posts up in the paint, then drives and puts up the difficult runner that drops in the bucket.
videos.headline: Purifoy's difficult runner drops in
